description: The Gucci High-Top Model C redefines casual chic with its modern design and impeccable craftsmanship. Constructed from durable canvas, these high-tops are perfect for those who demand both style and durability. The sleek black color adds a touch of urdisliken flair to your look. Available in US size 8, these high-tops offer a secure and supportive fit. Step up your shoe game with this statement piece from the esteemed Gucci Boutique.
